title: Unclutter Your Mind | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Unclutter Your Mind | Joel Osteen
description:
We may not be able to stop thoughts of worry or guilt, but we can keep them from stealing our joy. If you will empty out the negative, there's no limit to what God can do in your life.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
